msgstr "Wesnoth 歴 1095 年"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:7
msgid ""
"At a great battle at the Stone of Erzen, the brothers Gwiti and Nati Ha’atel "
"showed their skills for the first time: thinking that their side was losing "
"the battle, they called upon the corpses of former enemies to rise again and "
"fight on their side."
msgstr ""
"Erzen の石での大戦において、Gwiti と Nati Ha’atel の兄弟は初めて彼らの力を披"
"露した。自分達の陣営が戦いに破れそうだと考えた彼らは、倒れた敵を蘇えらせ、仲"
"間として戦わせたのであった。"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:11
msgid ""
"However, not only was this forbidden, but rash as well. The cavalry meant to "
"come as reinforcements instead clashed with the undead legions, and so the "
"battle was lost where it would have been won had it not been for these two "
"dark sorcerers."
msgstr ""
"しかしながら、これは禁じられていただけでなく、性急過ぎでもあった。騎兵隊が増"
"援軍として参加するつもりが、代わりにこのアンデッド軍団と衝突してしまい、この"
"二人の降霊術師がいなければ勝てていたはずのその戦いは、敗北を喫する事となっ"
"た。"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:15
msgid ""
"The Ha’atel brothers fled. However, they were seized by the Wesnothians not "
"long after. They were clapped in irons, marched onto a ship with no rudder, "
"and sent off to drown in the sea, for the Wesnothians feared that their "
"corpses might only rise again."
msgstr ""
"Ha’atel 兄弟は逃げたが、直ちに Wesnoth 人に捕らえられた。彼らは、鉄の足かせで"
"舵のない船の上まで歩かさせられ、海の底へと沈めるために送り出された。Wesnoth "
"人は、二人の亡骸が再び蘇える事を恐れたのである。"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:19
msgid ""
"But Fate intervened. The ship carrying Gwiti and Nati was beset by a sudden "
"storm and disintegrated, separating the brothers and washing them both "
"ashore. This was the beginning of the Rise of the Dark Hordes."
msgstr ""
"だが運命は逆転した。Gwiti と Nati を乗せたその船は突然の嵐に巻き込まれて分解"
"し、兄弟を離れ離れにして、岸に押し流した。これこそ、暗黒の大軍団の蜂起の始ま"
"りであった。"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:28
msgid ""
"Gwiti found the survivors of the coastal cult who had been hiding and "
"brought them under his control. They had lost sight of their respective "
"goals, along with their master, but the accursed being who had suddenly "
"appeared claimed to lead them."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:32
msgid ""
"As Gwiti explored the unknown land with Arkal-Thil, he ran into his brother."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:40
msgid "Still wandering the unknown land, Gwiti entered lands of the Orcs."
msgstr "依然、謎の土地を探索していると、Gwiti はオーク族の国に入り込んだ。"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:44
msgid ""
"They all bore skull-topped banners. But one of these skulls was special..."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:53
msgid "1096 YW"
msgstr "Wesnoth 歴 1096 年"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:54
msgid ""
"Furious at the Skull’s lack of power, Gwiti decided to seize a different "
"artifact, the Book of Crelanu."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:63
msgid ""
"According to the journal Gwiti recovered, after the death of Delfador the "
"Great, the tradition was started to entrust the Book with the King’s closest "
"advisor."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:66
msgid ""
"This turned out to be a costly mistake, sparking the greatest undead "
"invasion Wesnoth had ever seen."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:70
msgid ""
"After this, no mage dared take guardianship of the Book. Instead, they "
"decided to hide Crelanu’s work where none would find it, while spreading "
"rumors that it was guarded in the Tower of Kaleon."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:73
msgid ""
"Five centuries later, Gwiti retraced their steps, which led him to a war-"
"torn valley."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:82
msgid "1097 YW"
msgstr "Wesnoth 歴 1097 年"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:83
msgid ""
"However, the march of Gwiti was reported to Wesnoth by one of the scouts who "
"had seen him."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:91
msgid ""
"Gwiti and Tanar rushed into the maze of twisting little passages, quickly "
"leaving the humans behind. But not much later, they ran into dwarves..."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:99
msgid ""
"Crossing the pool did not take long and soon the orcs and undead marched on "
"through the damp cave, into the mountain. While the orcs shivered in the "
"magical air, Gwiti spent some time reading the Tome."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:108
msgid ""
"The orcs and undead easily defended the cave stronghold and when the water "
"subsided, the nagas were driven off or slain, their magical artifact "
"exhausted."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:111
msgid "And the long months passed..."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:119
msgid "1099 YW"
msgstr "Wesnoth 歴 1099 年"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:120
msgid ""
"Gwiti finished studying the Tome of Crelanu and departed for where he "
"believed the other half of Morgorath’s skull to be. The orcs, restless "
"without an enemy to fight, eagerly followed."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:129
msgid ""
"Gwiti’s research directed him north, further into the orcish lands. "
"Eventually, he could sense the presence of the skull’s other half. The "
"feeling led him to what appeared to be an orcish capital."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:138
msgid ""
"Tanar decided to use the death of the would-be Great Chiefs to subject the "
"local tribes to his own rule. Plans to jointly invade Wesnoth were discussed."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:141
msgid ""
"Gwiti knew that as long as paladins and magi roamed the land, any invasion "
"would be severely hindered. So he decided to strike at the source of his "
"problems: Alduin."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:150
msgid ""
"With the magi out of the way, Gwiti was ready to begin his invasion, "
"starting at the city of Aldril."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:159
msgid ""
"Unknown to Gwiti, several magi present on Alduin had survived his attack. "
"Faced with a danger beyond their own ability, they contacted outside help, "
"the slayer of the Necromancer-Emperor."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:167
msgid ""
"After defeating Elynia, Gwiti aimed for Weldyn. In the middle of his march "
"route was the city of Dan’Tonk."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:175
msgid ""
"An unexpected confrontation with Morgorath weakened Gwiti’s forces. He fled "
"to the northeast, deciding to proceed in hiding into Glyn’s Forest."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:183
msgid "1100 YW"
msgstr "Wesnoth 歴 1100 年"

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:184
msgid ""
"Gwiti survived being turned on by the orcs and managed to escape eastwards."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:188
msgid ""
"The Northern Alliance had sent military aid and with two armies hunting for "
"him, Gwiti was trapped in the Estmarks."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:191
msgid ""
"He spent months evading patrols while trying to build his strength back up. "
"Eventually, he was hunted down by a rather familiar elf."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:199
msgid ""
"But shortly before his doom, Gwiti was transported to another realm by an "
"unknown power..."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: TDH/macros/storytxt.cfg:202
msgid "And then he awoke."
msgstr ""

