msgid "Death of Gwiti Ha’atel"
msgstr "Gwiti Ha’atel の死"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:127
msgid ""
"After his banishment from Wesnoth for practicing necromancy, the young Gwiti "
"Ha’atel arrived on a strange shore. He decided to claim it for his own."
msgstr ""
"降霊術を学んだ為に Wesnoth から追放された後、若い Gwiti Ha’atel は奇妙な海岸"
"へ辿り着いた。彼はそこを自分のものとする事を決意した。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:132
msgid ""
"Apparently the gods have not yet completely abandoned me. The smell of the "
"beast is in the air around here — perhaps they are the material for testing "
"whether I shall survive."
msgstr ""
"どうやら神々はまだ完全に私を見捨ててはいないようだ。この辺りには獣の臭いがす"
"る。おそらく私が生き延びられるかどうかを試す材料となるだろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:136
msgid ""
"Not sure why, but this ruin is filled with bones and souls... as if the dead "
"bearing their regrets were waiting for me. This is to my convenience."
msgstr ""
"何故だか分からないが、この廃墟には骨と魂が満ちている... まるで無念を抱えた死"
"者達が私を待っていたかのようだ。これは私にとっては、好都合だ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:144
msgid ""
"But I only wonder where my brother has disappeared to. Do the gods know that "
"one surviving Ha’atel is enough?"
msgstr ""
"だが兄弟がどこに消えたのか気になる。神々は一人の Ha’atel だけが生き残れば十分"
"だと考えているだろうか？"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:152
msgid ""
"These monsters are not worthy of being real opponents with whom I should "
"confront. Even their souls shall serve my power."
msgstr ""
"これらの怪物は私が向き合うべき真の敵となる価値もない。彼らの魂すら私の力とな"
"るだろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:156
msgid "Where do we go from here, master?"
msgstr "我らはどこへ向かうのですか、主人よ？"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:160
msgid ""
"I must seek for Nati, for I do not believe he perished as a prey to the "
"waves. Though my brother, he was always my obstacle. If he lives... he will "
"eventually stand before me."
msgstr ""
"私は Nati を探さねばならない。彼が波の餌食となって死んだとは信じられん。彼は"
"私の兄弟だが、常に私の障壁でもあった。彼もまた生きていれば... いずれ我が前に"
"現れるだろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:164
msgid ""
"By the way, new master... there must be other brethren hiding besides me."
msgstr "ところで、新しい主人... 私以外にも隠れている同朋がいるはずなのです。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:168
msgid ""
"Your brethren? Looking back, the naga I killed also said some strange "
"remarks. What transpired here?"
msgstr ""
"お前の同朋？思い返せば、私が倒したナーガも奇妙な事を言っていた。ここで何が"
"あったのだ？"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:172
msgid ""
"This beach was sacred ground for our cult, seekers of death’s power. But "
"beasts attacked, our master’s strength failed... the rest were slaughtered, "
"and the few survivors hid in shadows."
msgstr ""
"この浜辺は死の力を求める我らの教団の聖地でした。しかし獣どもが襲い、我らの師"
"は力尽き... 残りの者たちは殺され、僅かな生存者は影に隠れました。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:176
msgid ""
"Well, now I knew why there had been so many traces of death when I arrived. "
"But now, the monsters that plagued you are destined to rise again as our "
"puppets... right?"
msgstr ""
"なるほど、私が到着した時に、あれ程に多くの死の痕跡があった理由が分かったぞ。"
"だが今や、お前達を悩ませた怪物どもは我らの操り人形として再び立ち上がる運命に"
"ある... そうだろう？"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:192
msgid "Argh! I die!"
msgstr "ああ！私は死ぬ！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:206
msgid "Death is good for the nagas that bother me!"
msgstr "私を邪魔するナーガどもには死がお似合いだ！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:217
msgid ""
"Where did he come from? We were supposed to have destroyed the cult in this "
"area!"
msgstr "奴はどこから現れた？この地域の教団は全て、壊滅させたはずだったのに！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:221
msgid "Cult? What is your saying?"
msgstr "教団？何を言っている？"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:233
msgid ""
"Oops, there is someone hiding. Those who hide in the shadows of battle are "
"doomed to a miserable end..."
msgstr ""
"おや、誰か隠れているな。戦いの影に隠れる者は、惨めな最期を迎える運命にあるが…"

#. [unit]: id=Arkal-Thil, type=Dark Adept
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:239
msgid "Arkal-Thil"
msgstr "Arkal-Thil"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:259
msgid ""
"Spare my life, I beg you! I was about to be devoured by them, but your "
"darkness saved me..."
msgstr ""
"命乞いをします！あの者どもに喰らわれるところでしたが、あなたの闇が私を救って"
"くれました..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:264
msgid ""
"Are you of my own kind? If you want mercy and more necromancy, come with me. "
"Obey me and you will become more mighty."
msgstr ""
"お前は私と同類か？慈悲と死霊術をさらに求めるなら、私と共に来るがいい。私に従"
"えば、さらにお前は強大になれるだろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:269
msgid ""
"I sense power within you. The potential to surpass my father... I pledge "
"myself to your hordes."
msgstr ""
"あなたの中に力を感じます。私の父を超える可能性を... あなたの軍勢にこの身を捧"
"げましょう。"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:283
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:90
msgid "Death of Arkal-Thil"
msgstr "Arkal-Thil の死"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:302
msgid "Noooo! Not now, not when I have escaped!"
msgstr "そんな！今、脱出したばかりだったのに！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:316
msgid "Oh no! Am I foolish enough to obey him, and die like this?"
msgstr "ああ！彼に従い、こんな風に死ぬとは愚かだった！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/01_A_New_Chance.cfg:327
msgid "The Wesnothians have discovered my escape! This is not good..."
msgstr "Wesnoth 人どもは私の脱走に気づいた！これはよくないぞ..."

#. [scenario]: id=02_Brother_Against_Brother
