msgstr "兄弟 Nati Ha’atel を倒す"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:121
msgid ""
"As the sun set, Gwiti discovered that his arch-rival and brother, Nati, had "
"already ensconced himself nearby."
msgstr ""
"日が沈むと、Gwiti は彼の弓のライバルであり、兄弟である Nati がそばに潜んでい"
"た事に気づいた。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:126
msgid ""
"Ah, hated brother mine. Look well upon the setting sun, for you shall not "
"live to see another in this land."
msgstr ""
"あぁ、憎まれし我が兄弟よ。沈む太陽を見よ、そなたはこの国では二度と、生きて見"
"る事はないのだ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:130
msgid ""
"This land? Do you truly not know where we are? Then you are a greater fool "
"than I had thought."
msgstr ""
"この国、だと？お前は本当に、我らが何処にいるか分からぬのか？ならばそなたは、"
"俺が思っていた以上の愚か者だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:134
msgid ""
"Cease your blustering; the darkness shall always be upon my side. You must "
"die to prove it."
msgstr ""
"口のきき方には気をつけるがよい、闇は常に我が陣営にあるのだから。そなたはその"
"証として死すのだ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:138
msgid ""
"I will fight you with all my strength to prevent that, and I was always the "
"stronger of us. Flee now and save your miserable hide before I make it a "
"carpet."
msgstr ""
"それを防ぐため、全力を尽くしてお前と戦おう。私は常にお前よりも強かった。今す"
"ぐ逃げ出して、敷物にされる前にみじめな隠れ家を守るがよい。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:162
msgid ""
"Don’t be silly! I’m not hairy enough to be a carpet! But your scalp would "
"make a good pillow."
msgstr ""
"馬鹿を言うな！敷物になるほど毛も生えておらぬわ！だが、お前の頭皮は良い枕にな"
"るであろう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:166
msgid "Master, are you going to destroy your blood brother?"
msgstr "師匠、血を分けた兄弟を滅ぼすつもりですか？"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:170
msgid ""
"One master leading the undead hordes is enough. And what choice would you "
"make if you were in my shoes? Either you sacrifice yourself by insisting on "
"flimsy brotherhood, or..."
msgstr ""
"不死の軍勢を率いる者は一人で充分だ。もしくは、お前が私の立場ならば、取る選択"
"は何か？薄っぺらい兄弟愛を主張して自身を犠牲とするか、それとも..."

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:174
msgid "I would obviously choose the latter too, as you say."
msgstr "私は明らかに後者を取るでしょう、仰せのままに。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:185
msgid "What? I can’t die! I already have! Noooo!"
msgstr "何だと？私は死ねない！既に死んでおる！そんな馬鹿な！"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:189
msgid ""
"Ha ha ha, did I not tell you it would be so? Perhaps I shall summon your "
"shade to serve me one day. Until then... farewell!"
msgstr ""
"ハハハ、そうなると言わなかったか？おそらく私はいつの日かお前の影を召喚し、私"
"に仕えさせるであろう。その時まで... さらばだ！"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:193
msgid "It is over. I am doomed."
msgstr "終わった。私の運は尽きた。"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:204
msgid "Your doom is at hand!"
msgstr "お前の破滅は目前だ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:215
msgid ""
"His legions are nothing more than a hodge-podge... It is only the matter of "
"time before I beat him."
msgstr ""
"彼の軍団は寄せ集め以上の何でもない... 私が奴を打ち負かすまで時間の問題だ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Arkal-Thil
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:219
msgid ""
"Very well. I am not sure if the showdown will end this evening, but you will "
"surely be the last one standing."
msgstr ""
"結構です。対立がこの夜に終るかは分かりませんが、最後に立っているのは貴方で"
"しょう。"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:228
msgid ""
"You miserable wretch, know that it is only by my mercy that you look upon "
"the sun again, for you shall die before it sets."
msgstr ""
"慘めな下劣者よ、陽を再び拝めるのは、私の慈悲と思うが良い。陽が沈む前に死ぬの"
"だからな。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:232
msgid ""
"May I remind you that even as we speak, my undead legions are marching "
"towards you?"
msgstr ""
"我々が話した事を思い出せ。我が不死身の軍団は、そなたに向かって進軍しているだ"
"ろう？"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:243
msgid ""
"My foolish brother... Our doom began when we were born. You are just "
"slightly longer-lasting in your luck."
msgstr ""
"我が愚かな兄弟よ... 我らの破滅は誕生より始まっていたのだ。そなたはただ少しば"
"かり運が続いているだけだ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:247
msgid ""
"Is that all you want to say? I will surely stay alive and take revenge "
"against Wesnoth. You must go to the Land of the Dead and prepare to join my "
"hordes."
msgstr ""
"言う事はそれで全てか？俺は確実に生き残り、Wesnoth へ復讐を果たそう。貴様は死"
"者の国へ行き、我が軍団に加わる準備をしろ。"

#. [message]: speaker=Nati Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:252
msgid ""
"I curse you... You shall be killed like me and locked in a dream of darkness "
"forever."
msgstr ""
"お前に呪いを... お前は私と同じように殺され、そして暗闇の夢に永遠に閉じ込めら"
"れる。"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:268
msgid "Anyone who stands in my way will be burned to ashes!"
msgstr "私の道を邪魔する者は、皆、灰と化すのだ！"

#. [message]: speaker=Gwiti Ha'atel
#: TDH/scenarios/02_Brother_Against_Brother.cfg:282
msgid "Now you shall die!"
msgstr "今こそ、お前は死ぬのだ！"

#. [unit_type]: id=Deathmaster, race=human
#: TDH/units/Deathmaster.cfg:5
msgid "Deathmaster"
msgstr "死人使い"

#. [unit_type]: id=Deathmaster, race=human
#. [unit_type]: id=Grimreaper, race=human
#: TDH/units/Deathmaster.cfg:19 TDH/units/Grimreaper.cfg:21
msgid ""
"His wanderings on a dark path have given him power normally not granted to "
"mortals, but with a terrible cost: the undead that he gave his soul to are "
"gradually claiming his mortal shell too, and with time, he will be a true "
"undead and a terror to all that lives."
msgstr ""
"彼は闇の小径で彷徨う事によって、通常では人間には得られない力を与えられました"
"が、その代償は恐るべきものです。彼が魂を与えた不死の者は、次第に彼の精神に忍"
"び込んでおり、時を経て、彼は完全な不死の者となり、生ける者全てから恐れられる"
"ようになるでしょう。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demilich, race=undead
#: TDH/units/Demilich.cfg:5
msgid "Demilich"
msgstr "デミリッチ"

#. [unit_type]: id=Demilich, race=undead
#: TDH/units/Demilich.cfg:25
msgid ""
"After too much time dabbling with forbidden magics and dark arts, these magi "
"have begun to pay a heavy price. Demiliches have started losing their "
"bodies, becoming undead themselves. With time, they may become fully undead, "
"and feared by all alike."
msgstr ""
"禁断の魔術と黒魔術にあまりにも長く関わった事で、この魔術師は重い代償を払い始"
"めています。デミリッチは肉体を失い始めており、不死の者に変わりつつあります。"
"時を経て、彼等は完全に不死の体となり、生ける者全てから恐れられるようになるで"
"しょう。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dread Lich, race=undead
#: TDH/units/Dread_Lich.cfg:5
msgid "Dread Lich"
msgstr "恐怖のリッチ"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dread Lich, race=undead
#: TDH/units/Dread_Lich.cfg:26
msgid ""
"At long last, Ha’atel has paid the ultimate sacrifice for the dark arts into "
"which he has delved, and has, himself, entered into undeath. At the apex of "
"his power, he has become a lich, a waking embodiment of dread. He has, "
"beyond any doubt, passed the point of no return, and his power and "
"immortality will have to provide consolation for what he has lost in his "
"quest to achieve them."
msgstr ""
"遂に Ha’atel は暗黒の芸術に対して彼が探求してきた事へ究極の犠牲を払い、彼自身"
"不死の存在へと足を踏み入れました。彼の力の頂点で、歩く恐怖の権化リッチへと変"
"わったのです。彼は全く疑いなく、もう戻れない一線を超え、彼の力と不死はそれを"
"成し遂げるために彼の冒険で失ってきたものへの慰めをもたらすに違いないでしょ"
"う。"

#. [unit_type]: id=Grimreaper, race=human
#: TDH/units/Grimreaper.cfg:5
msgid "Grimreaper"
msgstr "死神"

#. [unit_type]: id=Initiate, race=human
#: TDH/units/Initiate.cfg:5
msgid "Initiate"
msgstr "下級術師"

#. [unit_type]: id=Initiate, race=human
#: TDH/units/Initiate.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Dabbling in the Death Magic, this young Ha’atel’s lust for power has "
"weakened him to the point where he is too weak to attack in regular combat."
msgstr ""
"死の魔術を少し触っただけのこの若い Ha’atel は、力への渇望により、通常の戦闘に"
"おける攻撃ができない程に弱くなっています。"
